# Project Setup Prompt

Set up the GrowCold monorepo from scratch based on the project specs.

## Read First
Before writing any code, read these files in order:
1. `CLAUDE.md` — stack, domain language, UX rules
2. `.cursor/rules/supabase-multitenancy.mdc` — tenant isolation patterns
3. `.cursorrules` — code style, file structure, offline-first patterns
4. `spec/COLD_STORAGE_MVP_CTO_SPEC.md` — business logic and domain model
5. `spec/API_AND_SCHEMA_SPEC.md` — database schema and API contracts
6. `spec/ARCHITECTURE_AND_DECISIONS.md` — technical decisions and rationale
7. `spec/FRONTEND_IMPLEMENTATION_GUIDE.md` — component patterns and state management
8. `spec/IMPLEMENTATION_CHECKLIST.md` — phased delivery plan

